data.description: **Motivated seller says price reduction and bring me offers!!** This private and quiet lovely home has a BRAND NEW METAL ROOF 2022 with transferrable 10 year warranty (pre-hurricane IAN!), IMPACT WINDOWS AND DOORS through out entire home, EXTREMELY well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage located in the City of North Port! Private garden of an assortment of fruits and vegetables started and currently growing, pick your own blueberries in your back yard! As you enter your screened front porch, coming from your walk way lined with privacy hedges, your front door enters right into the family gathering space.This generous sized living room is suitable for entertaining and warm cozy evenings for viewing your favorite shows. The gorgeous impact resistant sliding glass doors are situated right off the living room to enter your 16x9 screened in lanai over looking your private garden area. This garden area has been started with the most tender care and sweet touches, as well as a brand new trellis covering your brick pavers, great for out door cooking and gathering. The dining space in the kitchen also has impact slider glass doors right off the lanai area, with so many open and airy spaces, it's great for those cool Florida days. Stainless steel appliances through out your kitchen, with the enormous laundry room close by. This laundry room has had cabinets added for extra storage and brand new washer and dryer, purchased in 2022. Both guest rooms and guest bath are on the opposite side of the home from the master adding extra privacy for family or guests. You also have a formal dining space for those who like to entertain or use this space as a flex space for a small office. In the master bedroom you will find the room is fit for a king (bed)! And all of your other furnishings. The ensuite has double vanities, tub and walk in shower. There is also his and her walk in closets, for plenty of storage through out this home. Great location for those commuting to Sarasota or anywhere needing I-75, located just off Price Blvd and close to US 41, the heart of North Port, Warm Mineral Springs, Braves Stadium, The brand new Wellen Park, 776 and the spring training field, A rated schools, shopping, dining, medical and so much more!
